    <item>
      <title>픽셀북(모든 크롬북?)에서 Quake게임 실행하기</title>
      <link>https://bluedskim.github.io/posts/tech/%ED%81%AC%EB%A1%AC%EB%B6%81%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-quake%EA%B2%8C%EC%9E%84-%EC%8B%A4%ED%96%89%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0/index.html</link>
